# Assets Exposures Applications Received Amount

## identifier
de15086

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of a genuine application received for a finance facility made by a potential borrower. Sufficient information and/or relevant documentation have been submitted to allow for the application to be initially assessed.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.Exposures.ApplicationsReceived.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.19
- period=duration
